  "original_title": "SLT-MOBITEL continues nationwide tree planting programs",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "SLT-MOBITEL continues nationwide tree planting programs",
      "author": "Thilina Walpola",
      "body_lines": [
        "As part of its countless Environmental Social Governance (ESG) programs, SLT-MOBITEL carried out tree planting initiatives in Anuradhapura and Colombo recently. Themed \u2018Let\u2019s Nourish the Country with Clean Air and Fertilizer\u2019, SLT-MOBITEL embarked on the nationwide tree planting initiative with a pledge to improve air quality, reduce greenhouse gases and promote healthier soil for natural humidity control.",
        "The event launched in Colombo coincided with the 31st Anniversary of the Jathika Namal Uyana International Ecological Organization. H.M. Faizal Deen, Managing Director, Sat Co Lanka Technology (Pvt) Ltd. was the partner and donor of Meetrees at the event.",
        "Strengthening the initiative further, SLT-MOBITEL concluded yet another Mee Tree planting event at the Sri Maha Bodhi premises in Anuradhapura. Communities living in the Anuradhapura area received Meetrees from SLT-MOBITEL officials.",
        "SLT-MOBITEL selected the \u2018Mee\u2019 tree for the program considering its contribution to pest control, ability to be used in the production of organic manure, ability to purify the air and its use as a natural medicine. A significant feature of the tree planting program is the use of modern technology with the \u2018THURU\u2019 mobile application to monitor the progress of the project.",
        "SLT-MOBITEL firmly believes that this initiative contributes positively towards the protection of the environment and highlights the organisation\u2019s expansion of its Environmental Social Governance (ESG) responsibilities, as it moves forward into a more connected, secure, and sustainable future.",
        "Seylan Cards to ease insurance payments with easy payment plans",
        "Luminex officially enters the stock market with a listing on CSE",
